title: Wall Street Breakfast December 21: What Moved Markets This Week
author: Seeking Alpha
dc:creator: Seeking Alpha
description: Stocks rose further into record territory Friday, with the S&P 500 hitting an all-time high for a seventh straight session, amid continued optimism on resolving the U.S.-China trade war and strength in domestic consumer spending.
